<i>Epeolus americanus</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Phileremus americanus </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Phileremus montanus </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Epeolus montanus </i>&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;; <i>Epeolus lanhami </i>Mitchell, 1962</small><p>
